data.text:
Then we conveniently defeat a powerful wizard by dropping him into a pit. and that's the b plot in this game. Now to save our sister.

That was uninvited a short horror themed point and click adventure game from the early days of gaming. A blast with the past may not be perfect but has enough puzzle solving to take an evening of your time.

Uninvited is a horror-themed point-and-click adventure game developed originally for the Macintosh by ICOM Simulations released in 1986 by Mindscape.

The game uses the MacVenture engine that was introduced in ICOM's prior game, Deja Vu: a Nightmare Comes True.
